<h4 style="font-family:'Libre Franklin',Arial,sans-serif;color:#5DA5DA
;text-align:center;">WELCOME TO THE SUN (6 of 6)</h4>
<hr />&nbsp;

<h1>The next steps for your Colorado Sun membership</h1>

<p><em>Your welcome to The Sun is over, but here&#8217;s a refresher on what we&#8217;ve learned and what&#8217;s next.</em></p>

</mj-text><mj-image src="https://lede-admin.coloradosun.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/15/2021/11/ferret-release-os-12.jpg?w=800" href="https://pico.link/thecoloradosun?short_code=upgrade" target="_blank"/><mj-text><p style="font-family:'Libre Franklin',Arial,sans-serif;color:#727273;padding:0 12px;margin:0;"><em>A black-footed ferret looks out from a prairie dog burrow after its release. (Olivia Sun, The Colorado Sun via Report for America)</em></span></p>

&nbsp;<hr />&nbsp;

<p>Thanks for sticking around through the end of The Sun&#8217;s welcome series. Now that we&#8217;re three weeks into sharing what else you need to know about the Sun, we&#8217;re about to set you free, with only periodic non-news updates.</p>

<p>What? You need a refresher? Here you go:</p>

<ol><li>Login — no password needed, though you can set one if you'd like — to our site to adjust your settings. Just press the &#8220;login&#8221; link at the top right or push the Sun logo in the bottom right of our site. If you&#8217;re not logged in, request &#8220;a magic link&#8221; and we&#8217;ll email you a link to get you logged in.</li><li>Pick your newsletters by pressing &#8220;Manage newsletters&#8221; or find out more on <a target="_blank"  href="https://coloradosun.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/360058798754-How-to-manage-The-Sun-s-newsletters"><strong>our FAQs</strong></a>.</li><li>Follow us on <a target="_blank"  href="https://twitter.com/ColoradoSun">Twitter</a>, <a target="_blank"  href="https://www.facebook.com/TheColoradoSun/">Facebook</a> or <a target="_blank"  href="http://instagram.com/thecoloradosun">Instagram</a> to get up-to-the-moment updates or converse with other Coloradans about Sun stories.</li><li>Check out our daily podcast on <a target="_blank"  href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/the-daily-sun-up/id1529487340">Apple Podcasts</a>, <a target="_blank"  href="https://open.spotify.com/show/5fBT1pSZB0ndSRmxbNNpaG?si=e96d547656a3427a">Spotify</a> or <a target="_blank"  href="https://coloradosun.com/podcast/?pico=clean">our website</a>.</li><li>We also <a target="_blank"  href="https://store.coloradosun.com/">have a store</a> with recently redesigned T-shirts. All profits go back into The Sun&#8217;s journalism.</li><li>We&#8217;re a <a target="_blank"  href="https://coloradosun.com/annualreport/?pico=clean">public benefit corporation</a> incorporated with a mission to provide quality journalism to all Coloradans. We don&#8217;t want money to be an issue. That&#8217;s why our daily newsletters and stories are free for anyone to access.</li><li>Your financial support makes this all possible. Revenue from memberships has already helped us expand our staff and cover a wider range of topics, from climate and equity to agriculture and rural economies.</li><li>Become a basic, basic+ or premium member by visiting <a target="_blank"  href="https://coloradosun.com/welcome?pico=clean">coloradosun.com/welcome</a>.</li></ol>

<p>We&#8217;re glad you&#8217;re here and reading and we hope you&#8217;ll join us as a member!</p>

